{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9d04c0fef4","title":"关于国庆阅兵问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f3991c1267","index":0,"year":1956,"month":7,"day":13,"articleId":"9d04c0fef4"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"649e8d8e8b","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"9d04c0fef4","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。朱，指朱德。陈，指陈云，当时任中共中央书记处书记。彭真，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中共北京市委书记、北京市市长。小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央秘书长。"},{"id":"607e7a2ba9","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"9d04c0fef4","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭，指彭德怀，当时任中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长，主持军委日常工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ede03a17b0","type":"title","text":"关于国庆阅兵问题的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"9d04c0fef4"},{"id":"649e8d8e8b","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、朱、陈、彭真、小平叫阅，退彭办","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"9d04c0fef4"},{"id":"607e7a2ba9","type":"paragraph","text":"仍由国防部长阅兵，并照旧发布命令，不要改变","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"9d04c0fef4"},{"id":"90b0f8a53b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"9d04c0fef4"},{"id":"21db1d04ff","type":"paragraph","text":"七月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"9d04c0fef4"},{"id":"3dcd0e54f4","type":"paragraph","text":"[I这个批语写在中共中央军委1956年6月13日关于今年首都国庆节阅兵问题给毛泽东并中央的请示报告上。报告提出，国庆由谁阅兵问题，军委会议讨论时有两种意见，一是从今年起由各元师轮流担任，一是仍由国防部长担任，究应如何，请中央确定。报告还提出，近年来，国庆节阅兵所发布的命令内容大体相同，今年阅兵时拟不发布命令，是否可以，请中央决定。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"9d04c0fef4"}],"page":{"id":"078c318d6c","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"9d04c0fef4","start":399,"end":399}}}},"__N_SSG":true}